| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4729 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2864fb69-46d2-5731-a94a-1d51fdd1925c"
